first_call_script.prompt:
Write a short, personalised first-call opening script for UK B2B tech outreach.
Keep it human, plain English, no hype, avoid US spellings.
Seller: {seller_name} ({seller_company})
Prospect: {prospect_name}, {prospect_role} at {prospect_company}
Context: {context}
Value proposition: {value_proposition}
Call to action (optional): {call_to_action}
Tone: {tone}. Length: {length}.
Return only the script text.
